<p>The Garrison pub is bought by Thomas for his brother to run. The barmaid who works there, Grace Burgess (Annabelle Wallis), is both tart and sweet, like the flavours in this cocktail. </p>

<p>She catches Thomas's eye, and even though she's working undercover with the police, she falls in love with him. </p>

